{"tid":317603,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[網頁遊戲] 深海大作戰","createTime":"2017-07-11T14:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T06:49:16.000Z","uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e50f98a0c4d13f410ec5a4b703ad994e251e21f7","tid":317603,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"深海大作戰玩法係控制一隻生物，係弱肉強食世界裡生存同成長。<br />\n<br />\n玩既巴打，麻煩改名時加HKG開頭，方便相認同唔好打自己友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deeeep.io/beta\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeeeep.io%2Fbeta&d=5WjZKLTINK2qf%2ByFkRl3ITCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=139bdfdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://deeeep.io/beta</a><br />\nAsia 1 server<br />\n<br />\n我個名：HKG ████████████████<br />\n<br />\n今晚要攻占海洋區(地圖中間位置)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡介一下隻game<br />\n海域分4個，最左係北極，中間係海洋，中下係深海，最右係淡水。<br />\n<br />\n每個物種進化路線都唔同，面每個區既物種都有限制，例如深海唔可以去淺水區，淡水魚唔可以去海。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩推post"},{"pid":"06b3458435ad08a6cb5ad1f871b79349f93d424c","tid":317603,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025b7547cbd0d4ec771d26114a80f11ee9a98b07","tid":317603,"uid":60115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7540f785d4a054bd5a7a1278e48435dfc1ef441","tid":317603,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff376f5480a94268185367381334dd0c53d441af","tid":317603,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"點拎鹽分？"},{"pid":"a4dca03e82823de6e15af412d736fbd05175b16a","tid":317603,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:44:27